{"tid":2439524,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"熊田曜子餵人奶長達六年 自爆G Cup胸縮水兼走樣","createTime":"2021-03-09T10:06:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T12:07:23.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"947e16fa124938643d9810d98da4592fac610279","tid":2439524,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/T4gACJe-WQZGl3ScZnadjCA-AeU=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BQUATNBEIJEC3EFXSCKU3B2LKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FT4gACJe-WQZGl3ScZnadjCA-AeU%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBQUATNBEIJEC3EFXSCKU3B2LKU.jpg&h=7e3444a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n38歲日本女星熊田曜子一向以性感見稱，曾經對G Cup雙乳自豪的她，近日在IG剖白餵人奶長達六年的辛酸，自爆上圍走樣，令她感到厭惡，目前正積極接受健身訓練，望把胸部改善成為最理想型態。<br />\n<br />\n熊田曜子育有三個囡囡，她於2012年結婚後誕下大女，分別於2015和2018年再做媽咪，由於細女終於戒奶，使熊田曜子可以結束長達六年的餵母乳生涯，並在IG上表示：「對於有三個小孩，每個都餵母乳兩年來養育，當戒奶後，胸部縮水令我感到驚訝&hellip;20多歲時為之驕傲的胸部，形狀與彈性已完全不同...」如今熊田曜子照鏡卻十分討厭自己的胸部，故目前她決定花兩個月時間靠運動來健胸，並在其YouTube頻道分享成果。<br />\n<br />\n熊田曜子能keep住驕人身材並不容易，為了保養搵食架生，她透露從中學開始每日會做200次美胸體操，就連著名內衣品牌「PEACH JOHN」最近也找她擔任內衣模特兒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5uH_jafbfrSth6Bhs2MMYViheW0=/802x507/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AVETNL3ASVCWNLYBPLEA2M7HFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5uH_jafbfrSth6Bhs2MMYViheW0%3D%2F802x507%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAVETNL3ASVCWNLYBPLEA2M7HFM.jpg&h=2b6f432b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PqLSgqUE-ktQBfiwEELR79jOE6k=/802x991/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L5E2KA6WPRC5NP4NLIDRFED5KU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPqLSgqUE-ktQBfiwEELR79jOE6k%3D%2F802x991%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL5E2KA6WPRC5NP4NLIDRFED5KU.JPG&h=ce2b7501&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TaMINp6ieFoAtFXuWbcSrHxVxO8=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WC5FEZG6QRCHTGX32K5QIPMRZI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTaMINp6ieFoAtFXuWbcSrHxVxO8%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWC5FEZG6QRCHTGX32K5QIPMRZI.JPG&h=145a7210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bdiPPzHWbFfDqnnjkbJv5VquXRM=/802x450/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/32DIH6XAZNB4HAQAIKSXU2MOD4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbdiPPzHWbFfDqnnjkbJv5VquXRM%3D%2F802x450%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F32DIH6XAZNB4HAQAIKSXU2MOD4.JPG&h=0ddba6bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mbvscQkTpYPZlyT61Ij4eAtM6xE=/802x1224/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WIPEWPOU6BBHBC2KSVYVDBBKZI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmbvscQkTpYPZlyT61Ij4eAtM6xE%3D%2F802x1224%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWIPEWPOU6BBHBC2KSVYVDBBKZI.JPG&h=7f499888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210309/CVUWNWJIG5DILAO4ENYJRFRUI4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210309%2FCVUWNWJIG5DILAO4ENYJRFRUI4%2